1Z.log` and `human-intervention-logs/org.aesh:readline:3.0/metadata-fix/codex.log`. Metrics were still written successfully in `stats/org.aesh/readline/3.0/execution-metrics.json`, which suggests the code/test changes progressed far enough to record coverage.\n\nManual next steps:\n1. Check out the preserved branch and rerun `generateMetadata` (or the nested `-Pagent test`) with a GraalVM JDK selected for the nested Gradle invocation so `native-image-agent` can be loaded.\n2. If that passes, rerun the same local CI checks from the preserved branch and verify the generated metadata/tests before opening a PR.\n3. If it still fails, inspect `human-intervention-logs/org.aesh:readline:3.0/metadata-fix/codex.log` together with the `native-test-verify/cycle-0-generateMetadata-*.log` files to confirm which JDK the nested build is using."}}
